  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nInccorect response of eth_estimateGas\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nThe request to Nethermind:\r\n`curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_estimateGas\",\"params\":[{\"from\":\"0xf76cFe9FcAFA43Ab5E1B74030BA329b291c545c9\",\"to\":\"0xd1ab46526d555285e9b61f066b7673bb9b9b51b6\",\"data\":\"\"}],\"id\":1}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" https://rpc.xdaichain.com/`\r\nreturns 0x166387a (23 476 346) - it is even higher that block gas limit.\r\nBut the same request sent to OpenEthereum node returns correct result:\r\n`curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_estimateGas\",\"params\":[{\"from\":\"0xf76cFe9FcAFA43Ab5E1B74030BA329b291c545c9\",\"to\":\"0xd1ab46526d555285e9b61f066b7673bb9b9b51b6\",\"data\":\"\"}],\"id\":1}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" https://xdai-archive.blockscout.com`\r\nreturns 0x6db46 (449350).\r\n",
